{
  "id": "RAW_cc931c",
  "title": "深度｜昆仑万维正成为全球化 AI 商业探索的中国样本，海外收入占比 91%，增长 22%",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/SbpWzRLibmMbpZLin3vO5g",
  "date": "2025-04-27 00:00:00",
  "author": "Z Potentials",
  "siteName": "Z Potentials",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"Z Potentials\" data-alias=\"ZPotentials\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/Z300vPwLQkkv763EiadS1eTfFnMp5Hm5eOAOX8AR81TFQM0azAFDNI8FLC15ITUMugG5sPQFR5icA7L1aGKWias3w/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"我们与Z Potentials同频共振\" data-id=\"MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile>\n  </section>\n  <h1 data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:24px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9z0cy2c15z2\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9z0cy4820ly\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">01 海外收入最多的中国 AI 企业</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">随着全球 AI 产业快速发展，海外市场已经成为各大 AI 企业争夺的核心战场。在这场国际化竞争中，昆仑万维（300418.SZ）以“海外收入最多的中国 AI 企业”的表现，正在全球 AI 产业版图中占据着独特且不可忽视的战略位置。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">根据昆仑万维于 2025 年 4 月 25 日发布的最新财报数据显示，2025 年公司实现营业总收入 56.6 亿元人民币，同比增长 15.2%，整体毛利率高达 73.6%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">最值得市场关注和分析的核心指标是昆仑万维在海外市场的强劲表现</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">：公司海外收入达到 51.5 亿元人民币，同比增长 21.9%，占总收入比重高达 91.0%，这一数据无疑标志着昆仑万维已经成为目前海外收入规模最大的中国 AI 企业之一，其国际化战略正在获得实质性的商业回报。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">分业务来看，各项业务数据也都表现亮眼。海外信息分发与元宇宙平台 Opera 实现 4.8 亿美元收入，同比增长 21.1%；海外社交网络和短剧平台收入 12.5 亿元，同比增长 28.5%，显示出公司在内容创作与社交领域的创新能力正在获得全球用户的认可和市场的回报。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">昆仑万维能够在海外市场取得如此显著的业绩增长，一方面源于其长期以来坚持的国际化发展战略和对海外市场的深刻理解，另一方面也得益于公司在 AI 技术领域的持续投入和创新能力，这使得昆仑万维能够将先进的 AI 技术与全球用户需求紧密结合，打造出具有国际竞争力的产品和服务。随着全球 AI 产业竞争的不断加剧，昆仑万维这种以海外市场为主要战场的发展模式，不仅为公司自身带来了可观的收入增长，也为中国 AI 企业参与全球竞争提供了宝贵的经验和参考。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">2024 年，昆仑万维的 AI 业务商业化在多个领域取得了突破，从初期的技术积累正转向实质性的收入贡献。AI 社交报告期内单月最高收入突破 100 万美元，成为海外收入增长速度最快的中国 AI 应用之一，AI 音乐年化流水收入 ARR 达到约 1,200 万美金（月流水收入约 100 万美金），短剧平台 DramaWave 年化流水收入 ARR 达到约 1.2 亿美金（月流水收入约 1000 万美金）。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:18px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI 短剧创作平台 「SkyReels」</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">昆仑万维以 AI 技术引领全球短剧行业进入普惠创作时代，2024 年 8 月推出集成视频与 3D 大模型的 AI 短剧创作平台「SkyReels」，实现全流程自动化创作，平台集成 SkyScript 剧本大模型、StoryboardGen 分镜生成大模型等多项自研技术，报告期内持续迭代模型能力，新增创意模板、写实 AI 演员、3D 交互编辑、AI 动捕等功能，2025 年初开源了视频生成模型 SkyReels-V1 和表情动作可控算法 SkyReels-A1，V1 支持 33 种表情与 400+种动作组合，截至 2</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">025 年 2 月，V1 在 Hugging Face 下载量近 3 万次，Github 获逾千星点赞，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">达到开源SOTA。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/76175958-92fc-473f-b324-2dacc2c0e000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4898148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100023363\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/76175958-92fc-473f-b324-2dacc2c0e000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9z0gold1akx\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9z0golw19oz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">DramaWave 产品界面展示</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:18px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9z0h52aitd\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9z0h5371692\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI 音乐创作平台「Mureka」</span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">昆仑万维在 2024 年 8 月推出海外AI音乐创作平台 Mureka，基于升级后的 SkyMusic 2.0&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">模型</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">（现 Mureka O1），打造</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">\"创作民主化+生态闭环\"的全新音乐创作方式。平台集成多语言歌词生成、音色克隆和精细编辑功能，让从业余爱好者到专业音乐人都能轻松完成全流程AI辅助创作。Mureka 构建了创作、分发、变现的完整生态，用户可通过积分系统创作音乐，获得版权保护，并在平台交易作品获利，同时开放 API 接口扩展应用场景，形成可持续发展的商业模式。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">截至 2025 年 3 月，Mureka 已取得显著的市场成绩，覆盖 100+ 国家/地区实现全球化布局，月访问量达 333 万，用户基础庞大。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI 音乐年化流水收入（ARR）达到约 1,200 万美金（月流水收入约 100 万美金）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/38b1525c-3154-4011-6a72-423afa358f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5370370370370371\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100023366\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/38b1525c-3154-4011-6a72-423afa358f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9z0hp4c1kax\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9z0hp554tx\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">Mureka 交互界面展示</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:18px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9z0i0bplec\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9z0i0d316dc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\">AI 社交应用「Linky」</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">社交方面，公司推出 AI 社交应用 Linky。Linky 的核心定位为虚拟角色互动与 UGC 生态平台，用户可创建自定义虚拟角色并通过文字、语音等多模态方式进行深度交互，应用场景涵盖情感陪伴、创意表达与社交技能训练。其商业模式结合订阅制（基础月费 9.99 美元）、抽卡机制（每 10 抽约 15 美元）及 UGC 创作者分成（角色粉丝超 100 且对话破万奖励 2 美元）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">作为昆仑万维\"AI+社交\"战略的旗舰产品，自上线以来，Linky 迅速打开全球市场，累计下载量突破 1,000 万次。展现出强劲的用户吸引力。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">截至报告期末，AI 社交业务单月最高收入突破 100 万美元/月，月活跃用户达到 300 万。</span></strong></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/77b24d94-6cc0-4fb1-f832-92da8ec95700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40925925925925927\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100023365\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/77b24d94-6cc0-4fb1-f832-92da8ec95700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9z0ieni1rqt\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9z0ienryjx\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">Linky 功能展示</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:18px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\">AI 游戏 「猫森学园」</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">昆仑万维自研AI游戏《猫森学园》(原《 Project G7 》)开发进展顺利。这款校园生活开放世界模拟游戏让玩家以高中新生身份探索校园与都市环境，与AI驱动的NPC互动体验丰富剧情。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">游戏最大亮点在于自由度极高的开放世界设计，玩家可定制角色、参与多样迷你游戏，并通过自由行动影响剧情发展</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">。游戏中的AI角色拥有真实情绪和记忆系统，能根据玩家行为做出个性化反应，大幅提升互动沉浸感。特色AI拍剧功能将 AIGC 技术转化为创意工具，玩家只需输入自然语言指令，系统便能自动完成从剧本构思到机位优化的全流程创作，智能匹配角色模型和动作序列，让内容创作变得简单而高效。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/897321e2-a347-445e-4e2c-f80d9861d300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5537037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1676\" data-height=\"928\" data-imgfileid=\"100023352\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/897321e2-a347-445e-4e2c-f80d9861d300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9z0jcw7srp\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9z0jcwr20u2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">《猫森学园》游戏场景展示</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:18px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\">AI 搜索 「天工AI 智能助手」</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">昆仑万维 2023 年 8 月率先推出国内首款AI搜索产品\"天工AI搜索\"，随后不断迭代升级为全能型AI智能助手。产品表现亮眼，报告期内\"天工\"峰值日活突破 100 万，月活用户超 1000 万。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">2024年2月，公司发布搭载 MoE 架构的千亿参数大模型应用\"天工AI智能助手\"，支持10万字超长上下文并引入多模态能力。随着产品持续进化，4月版本增添多轮搜索、图表绘制和研究模式等实用功能；下半年推出的高级搜索模式整合了海量专业数据资源，通过智能路径规划提供更全面的解答，同时文档分析能力大幅提升，可处理50万字超长文本。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">2024年底，公司基于天工大模型4.0重磅推出实时语音对话助手\"Skyo\"，采用端到端多模态建模技术，实现接近真人的自然对话体验，具备主动交流、长时记忆、多语言对话和情感化回复等先进功能。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:18px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\">短剧分发平台「DramaWave」</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">作为昆仑万维 AI 短剧生态的关键一环，公司于 2024 年下半年推出的 DramaWave 短剧平台与 SkyReels AI 创作平台形成了\"AI 创作+智能分发\"的完整闭环。DramaWave 采用\"付费+免费\"内容分发模式，通过提供 1080P 高清画质与多语言字幕支持，结合 AI 驱动的精准算法推荐机制为用户打造沉浸式观剧体验。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">DramaWave 不仅分发传统制作的优质短剧，更是 SkyReels 平台生成的 AI 短剧作品的主要展示窗口。平台内容涵盖从浪漫爱情到悬疑惊悚等丰富多样的短剧类型，满足用户碎片化时间的娱乐需求。SkyReels 通过其 SkyScript 剧本大模型、StoryboardGen 分镜生成大模型等自研技术，为 DramaWave 持续输送高质量内容，而 DramaWave 则通过其强大的分发能力，将这些 AI 创作的短剧推送给全球用户，实现技术到收入的高效转化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">DramaWave 平台市场表现亮眼，月活用户突破 1000 万，跻身行业前五，稳居出海短剧第一梯队。爆款剧《订婚风暴》5 天播放量破千万，助力平台 4 月登顶韩国 Google Play 娱乐应用榜首，连续霸榜四天超越 Netflix，彰显昆仑万维在 AI 短剧领域的强劲竞争力。截至 2025 年 3 月底，Dramawave 年化流水收入 ARR 达到约 1.2 亿美金（月流水收入约 1000 万美金）。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100023364\" data-ratio=\"0.45\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/60d32e95-684e-4874-43a3-c8fd6b91f300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/60d32e95-684e-4874-43a3-c8fd6b91f300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9z0js2mp3h\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9z0js311b66\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">DramaWave 韩国 Google Play 娱乐应用榜排名情况</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e2d0605f-a93e-45a2-17a1-436bc7489e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100023362\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e2d0605f-a93e-45a2-17a1-436bc7489e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\" mpa-font-style=\"m9z0ke3t5in\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9z0ke4sjpa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">DramaWave 产品界面展示</span></span></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:24px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">03 持续迭代的技术实力是核心动能</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">根据财报，昆仑万维 2024 年的研发投入达 15.4 亿元，同比增长 59.5%，这一战略性投入直接推动了公司在多个 AI 技术领域的突破。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">在大模型方面，公司的自研模型天工系列模型经历了多轮迭代升级，2 月推出基于 MoE 架构的\"天工 2.0\"，实现稀疏激活提升效率；4 月发布\"天工 3.0\"，参数达 4000 亿，性能提升 30%；11 月推出\"天工 4.0\"系列，包括专注实时语音交互的\"4o 版\"和具备慢思考推理能力的\"o1 版\"，展示了公司始终在模型研发的第一梯队。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">在音乐AI领域，昆仑万维的天工 SkyMusic 作为国内首款且唯一公开可用的 AI 音乐生成大模型，持续引领行业创新。初版模型(后更名为 Mureka )采用类 Sora 架构和 Large-scale Transformer 技术，实现了一体化端到端音乐生成，在音质和人声合成方面取得显著突破。随后推出的 SkyMusic 2.0 版本凭借自研 DiT 架构，在旋律连贯性、结构完整性和配器丰富度等方面实现质的飞跃，其人声音质、自然度和发音清晰度继续保持行业领先水平。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">公司在视频生成领域同样表现出色。为支持 AI 短剧创作，昆仑万维开发了专注于人物表情、动作与场景精准控制的视频生成模型，支持33种细腻表情与400多种动作组合。这些技术已成为公司AI短剧平台内容创作的核心引擎，显著提升了内容生产效率和质量，进而推动业务持续增长。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">在多模态处理领域，2025年3月，公司开源了 Skywork R1V 多模态思维链推理模型，成为中国首家开源多模态思考模型的企业。该模型采用创新的三阶段混合训练框架，成功将文本领域的顶尖推理能力迁移到视觉任务中。在 MMMU、MathVista 等权威评测中，其性能与规模更大的开源模型相当，甚至超越了部分主流闭源模型，达到业界一流水平。</span></p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:24px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">04 全球化 AI 商业探索的中国样本</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">昆仑万维的全球化布局是其区别于多数中国 AI 企业的核心优势。昆仑万维海外业务覆盖北美、欧洲、东南亚、中东等多个市场，积累了丰富的跨文化运营经验和本地化能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">在 AI 业务领域，昆仑万维展现出卓越的场景化应用能力。AI 短剧业务精准把握了韩国等亚洲市场的内容偏好，通过 AI 技术显著降低了优质内容的生产门槛和成本，实现快速市场渗透；AI 音乐领域则创造性地将创作平台与商业变现结合，有效解决了内容创作者的核心痛点；而 AI 社交产品通过提供智能聊天体验成功赢得海外用户青睐。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">昆仑万维在 AI 商业化道路上已走在大多数同行前列。在行业普遍仍专注于技术研发的阶段。昆仑万维通过技术创新、全球化运营和多元化应用落地，已构建从基础模型到应用产品的完整商业链条，实现了技术创新到收入转化的良性循环，也预示着未来几年可能实现更强劲的业绩增长。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;margin-right:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">对于行业观察者而言，昆仑万维提供了一个全球化 AI 商业探索的中国样本：不仅展现了技术实力的重要性，更证明了将中国互联网产品运营的敏捷性与全球化视野相结合的战略价值</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">。在全球 AI 竞争日益激烈的格局下，昆仑万维的成功路径或将成为中国企业出海的典范——以技术创新为基础，以场景化应用为抓手，以全球化思维为指引，打造具有持续增长潜力的 AI 商业帝国。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"white-space: normal;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__42\"><span leaf=\"\">-----------END-----------</span></span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space: normal;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==&amp;mid=2247506405&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=29bdac1ee34aaceade9e66e9b0867d8f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/Z300vPwLQkmMISOgKyml4wsGliaUpt2TbuDqbtPLty8Xa4uicSEHNRIr0TGkJmvqChgZNbN7OtwjSbzYFdFyv41g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_